The Marionette Collective
=========================

The Marionette Collective aka. mcollective is a framework to build server orchestration or parallel job execution systems.

For full information, wikis, ticketing and downloads please see http://marionette-collective.org/

New in Kontera's Version?
=========================
- Removed all 3rd party vendors, using gems instead.
- MCollective now can be packed into gem (rake gem).
- Installation of MCollective trough rubygems (gem install mcollective).
- New installer script available inside the gem, use it to install
-- MCollective Server
-- MCollective Client
-- MCollective Common Plugins


[root$] rake gem
